@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ertdup(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = wp.abs((0.41 * (tmp + 0.03 - v0 + 0.96)))
    v2 = 0.70
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.34 + tmp + 0.79) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.40)) * wp.cos(0.60))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
